#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:1
msgid "Welcome to Sync in Firefox 4 Beta"
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:3
msgid ""
"With Sync, you have instant access to all of your important Firefox data"
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:6
msgid "including your bookmarks, history, saved passwords and even open tabs"
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:8
msgid ""
"wherever you use Firefox, including on all of your computers and a growing "
"number of mobile phones."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:10
msgid "In a rush to leave but just found an interesting new website?"
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:12
msgid ""
"With Sync, you can pick up just where you left off at home, at work or on "
"the go – Just like magic."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:14
msgid "To enable Sync, you’ll need to create an account. So let’s get started."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:16
msgid ""
"When you download the latest version of Firefox 4 Beta, you'll be prompted "
"to create a Firefox Sync account"
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:18
msgid ""
"If you've been using Firefox Sync already, simply click “I’m already using "
"Sync on another computer” and log in. You're all set."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:20
msgid ""
"If this is your first time using Sync, click “I’ve never used Sync before”."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:22
msgid "Enter a username... password... and email address."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:24
msgid "Now create a secret phrase."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:26
msgid ""
"This 12 character or more phrase acts like the key to your safety deposit "
"box where only you have access to it."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:28
msgid "Don’t lose it since it protects your data."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:30
msgid "Click \"next\" unless you want to host the data on your own server."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:32
msgid "Type the words as they appear."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:36
msgid "Then click “Finish”. You now have a Firefox Sync account!"
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:38
msgid "Your Firefox data will start syncing in the background."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:40
msgid ""
"When you set up Sync for the first time, this might take a few moments, but "
"you can continue browsing the web."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:42
msgid ""
"Once the initial sync is complete, the rotating icon in the lower right "
"corner of your browser will change into the Sync icon."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:44
msgid ""
"From here on out, Sync will keep updating your data periodically to ensure "
"you stay in Sync."
msgstr ""

#: src-temp/includes/l10n/videos/sub-fx4-sync.html+div:46
msgid "Don't forget to set up Firefox Sync on all of your computers."
msgstr ""
